title: Brimheim - Exquisite Bliss (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Brinheim performing “Exquisite Bliss” live at Dypång, in Aarhus, Denmark, during SPOT Festival in May 2022.

Brimheim is Helena Heinesen Rebensdorff - Vocals / Guitar
Mads Haahr Andersen - Bass / Vocals 
Søren Manscher - Acoustic Guitar / Vocals 
Buster Jensen - Guitar / Synthesizer
Benedicte Pierleoni-Nielsen - Drums

Sound Engineer: Mathias Bang Madsen
Recording Engineers: Jonna Aspeklev & Rasmus Bredvig
Mix Engineer: Rasmus Bredvig at Tapetown / Lydhavnen
Assistant Mix engineer: Jonna Aspeklev
Mastering: Emil Thomsen at ET Mastering / Lydhavnen
Cameras: Claus Haargaard, Torsten Frøstrup, Christian Daugaard & Charlee Aurora
Production & Camera Assists: Charlina Mikkelsen, Juliane Eickstädt, Max Bülow Lassen, Asbjørn Lyhne, Søren Flecks & Morten Lovechild
Video Post Production/Edit: Rasmus Bredvig

KEXP at SPOT Festival was made possible by Music Export Denmark, SPOT Festival and ROSA, and with the kind support of the Danish Arts Foundation, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Denmark and the Ministry of Culture, Denmark. https://www.brimheim.com
https://spotfestival.dk/en
